snippet.title: Stahlfeder (Playstation)
snippet.description:
This one is pretty long... I didn't chop it because I had the luck of getting a no-hit full run on HARD. I guess this says a lot about how ridiculously easy the game is, right?

I used pilot Blau stern, with a default bullet color scheme (you can change the color of the bullets if you want).

Blog entry: http://1cclog.blogspot.com/2011/01/stahlfeder-playstation.html
